I"%<p><strong>Document Analytics directly on Compressed Data (VLDB’18, ICS’18, ICPP’19, ICDE’20) introduction of research projects</strong></p>

<p><img src="/assets/1.1.png" alt="fig 1.1" style="zoom:100%;" /></p>

<ul>
  <li>We propose the first known solution to enable direct document analytics on compressed data, which saves 90.8% storage space and 77.5% memory usage, while halving the analytics time.</li>
</ul>

<p><strong>Intelligent Programming in Heterogeneous Systems (MACSOTS’15, CGO’17, TPDS’17, TJSC’18, TKDE’19, ICPP’20, USENIX ATC’20)</strong></p>

<p><img src="/assets/1.2.png" alt="fig 1.2" style="zoom:120%;" /></p>

<ul>
  <li>We develop domain-specific languages, tools, and systems for heterogeneous processors, such as:</li>
  <li>FinePar: Fine-grained partitioning tool for irregular applications</li>
  <li>FineStream: Fine-grained stream processing system</li>
</ul>

<p><strong>Machine Learn Systems (IJCAI’20, ICPP’20, NPC’19, more papers are on the way)</strong></p>

<p><img src="/assets/1.3.png" alt="fig 1.3" style="zoom:70%;" /></p>

<ul>
  <li>We are designing novel deep learning algorithms and systems, such as PewLSTM (periodic LSTM with weather-aware gating mechanism), or ParSecureML (the first secure machine learning framework on GPUs).</li>
</ul>

